<body>
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>Scars</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <p>Wanna know how I got these scars???</p>
      <p>My father was a @Model.GetWord("occupation") and a fiend.</p>
      <p>So one night, he goes off crazier than usual. Mommy gets the @Model.GetWord("noun1") to @Model.GetWord("verb") herself.</p>
      <p>He doesn't like that. Not...one...bit. So, me watching, he takes the @Model.GetWord("noun1") to her, laughing while he does it.</p>
      <p>He looks at me, and he says <em>"@Model.GetWord("question") so @Model.GetWord("adjective")?"</em></p>
      <p>He comes at me with the @Model.GetWord("noun1"), <em>"@Model.GetWord("question") so @Model.GetWord("adjective") ?"</em></p>
      <p><em>"Let's put a @Model.GetWord("noun2") on that face!"</em></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-6">
      <img src="https://brobible.files.wordpress.com/2017/10/heath-ledger-joker-new-interviews-book.jpg?quality=90&w=626" alt="thejoker">
    </div>
  </div>
